Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能够听到“那个”的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是它正在对你说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能看到“那个”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么它就是你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:05 Distortion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类已经是不能进化的生物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突变机率比起动物是相当相当的低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫做雷欧典的人类说人类已经无法再进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类岂不成了低等动物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己都不知道凭什么推动进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类只会为了满足自己的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而驱使肉体行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会觉得无聊吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能如此地生存下去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.20,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已没必要再继续这种悲哀的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类已经找到一个脱离这世界的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类终于找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NETWORK 也就是网络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点东西好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不饿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说一句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你要听什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我一些我不知道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道的事根本不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法告诉你不存在的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这么说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的发生其实是先有预言的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了预言 这些事才会成真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？ 谁会预言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.56,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京各地区V, T, C, Z, X, 交通号志出现错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是在塞车的的路口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.00,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私家车和货车的自动行驶系统都受到干扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致多宗车辆暴冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京的涉谷一带特别严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车祸引致较多人受伤 情报管理局…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.56,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚收到最新的消息 系统已回复正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 有空吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快抹干 会洗不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(地狱已经没有位置 亡魂已失去容身之处)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不吉利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？ 讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 预言终于要实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这样的话 就不是预言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是预言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是时间轴上的各点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.80,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结起来的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们都是以线联系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说全都可能被线联系着会比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？ 被谁联系着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到 原来你如此了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 看来你已能发挥自己的本能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再装傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的…不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你做的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午 网络通讯系统所发生的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人为因素很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报管理局已开始全面调查此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.00,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏网络通讯系统是一项刑事罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪者会受到严厉的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,948元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 请慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是垃圾邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱传的电子邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指预言实现的电子邮件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是邪教的宣传手法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早阵子在网上跟朋友谈论过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邮件像是由KNIGHTS发出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS？ 是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是网络上专家级骇客集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 骇客是不会一起行动的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.50,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说没错 但因为是KNIGHTS可能会不一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它在网络上拥有很大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 它不就是地下集团？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 做这种事会有趣吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只觉得他们的所作所为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为好玩或金钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络和现实世界基本上是相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.00,0:13:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界的肉体之类的东西\N只不过是网络上流传的程序罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.30,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本人的肉体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体的脑部活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是由电流传导所引发的非常普通的物理现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体存在的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.30,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是确定自我的存在罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是不是我“真正”的妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前阵子你是否去过涉谷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过那位男生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你换了男朋友了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.20,0:16:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(预言实现)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？ 什么预言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈总是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.13,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(把预言实现)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是我爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网络上流传的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不是单纯的电子档案而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络是因为电话之类的电器产品等等所发展而形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.33,0:19:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我们就不得不注意到这时就会形成另一个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实世界内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的存在只是概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在网络上的世界就不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概念可以被肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不知道该不该称他为神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.10,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少他能拥有跟神话中的神一样的超自然力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能曾经在网络上和神说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是在网络上以这真神的支配力来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力有可能随意介入现实世界中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是以预言这个形式介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.80,0:21:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会是谁呢？
